  <id>org.zirael.bkchem.BKChem</id>
  <name>BKChem</name>
  <summary>Molecule drawing program</summary>
  <developer_name>Beda Kosata</developer_name>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-2.0</project_license>
  <description>
    <p>BKChem supports bond-bybond trying with templates. It supports linear fomulars, and a subset of SMILES as well as InChI. Arrows, rich text, color, charges, radicals and simple vector shapes can be used. It has aligning, unlimited undo/redo, rotation features. Export to SVG, OpenOffice Draw, ODF, EPS, PDF and PNG is possible. Basic support for CML1 and CML2 as well as Molfiles is available.</p>
  </description>
